<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
        
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>Please verify your email address {{.Email}} {{if .SessionName}}for device "{{.SessionName}}"{{end}}.</p>
        
        <p style="margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{.VerifyURL}}" style="background-color: #1D1D1D; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
                Verify Email
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>Brave Team</p>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
            <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p>{{.VerifyURL}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
